rows.label: qst701916_msg0001
rows.name:
I think I should come in very handy.
As a traveling artiste, I've seen a great
many places in my time.

rows.label: qst701916_msg0002
rows.name:
But...having said that, some places
are a little...difficult for me. There
was some...stuff.

rows.label: qst701916_msg0101
rows.name:
Friends! Iirans! Countrymen!
Lend me your assistance!

rows.label: qst701916_msg0102
rows.name:
I swear I will let Deetta down honestly
and maturely and free myself up to
truly give my all to Sarah!

rows.label: qst701916_msg0103
rows.name:
OK, yes, and we'll get the Dragon
Incense as well.

rows.label: qst701916_msg0201
rows.name:
I shall have to make tracks for the
capital shortly.

rows.label: qst701916_msg0202
rows.name:
Ohh, Sarah, my beloved! How my heart
aches to be by your side!
